snippet: Michael Phelps overhauled U.S. teammate Ryan Lochte late in their preliminary heat Sunday, qualifying for the 200 medley final at the Pan Pacific championships at the expense of his friend and long-time rival....

headline.print_headline: Phelps Into 200 IM Final at Pan Pacs; Lochte Out
headline.main: Phelps Into 200 IM Final at Pan Pacs; Lochte Out

lead_paragraph: Michael Phelps overhauled U.S. teammate Ryan Lochte late in their preliminary heat Sunday, qualifying for the 200 medley final at the Pan Pacific championships at the expense of his friend and long-time rival.
